diness.  Use this page to understand how to successfully partner with Career Services, promote and use its services, and how to tap into liaison relationships in the Career Services office.       Career Services Workshops   Career Services hosts a variety of career readiness workshops for students on a scheduled basis and on request basis.  To learn more about individual workshops and their learning objectives, launch the link below.  Staff/Faculty/Student Organizations: To request a Career Services workshop, click the request button below.    Career Services Workshop Descriptions    Upcoming Career Events         Career Services Workshop/Presentation Request Form      Suggested Career Readiness Activities for Campus Partners     Below are recommended activities campus partners can engage in to support students' career readiness skills.    Actions  Key Links      Promote ongoing career events and programs to students like career fairs (e.g., Diversity Fair, All Majors Fair)   Upcoming Career Events     Invite Career Services into your classroom or group meeting to present on career development and preparation topics Note:  Requests should be submitted at minimum 2 weeks in advance.   Career Services Workshop/Presentation Request Form     Post a job or internship on UICcareers.com    Post a Position Directions     Encourage students to schedule advising sessions or visit Career Services during drop-in hours to address career questions, get help with resumes/cover letters,  interviewing, among others.   Career Services Hours/Location     Please visit UIClife . To find Career Services updates and announcements, search on #UICCareerSvcs.   UIC Life     Share resource links with students to help them find jobs and internships.   Find a Job  Internships  Career Advising  Career Exploration   Resumes/CVs/Cover Letters   Networking     Connect with other Career Centers   Other Career Centers at UIC           Liaison Relationships   Stay tuned for updated information about staff members who serve as liaisons for colleges, units, and support services offices across UIC.  If you have a more immediate question on a liaison for your unit or college, please contact Career Services at (312) 996-2300.          Campus Partners    Back to main content           Career Services Workshop/Presentation Request Form                  UIC Logo        Career Services         Students    Career Planning Guide    Make an Appointment    FAQs      Employers    Post a Position    UICcareers.com      Campus Partners    Campus Partners    Program/Workshop Request Forms        Footer Menu    Career Programs and Events    UICcareers    UIC Student Employment Office         Contact   Suite 3050 1200 West Harrison Chicago, IL 60607  Phone: (312) 996-2300  Fax: (312) 413-0383  careerservices@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    YouTube             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 